text: Go, Diego, Go! is an American animated educational interactive children's television program. It premiered on Nickelodeon on September 6, 2005 in the United States. It was created and executive produced by Go Diego Go Dinosaurio Rescue Nintendo DS and Valerie Walsh Valdes. The series is a spin-off of Dora the Explorer. It follows Dora's cousin Diego, an 8-year-old boy. His adventures often involve rescuing animals and protecting their environment. ==Series overview== == Episodes == === Season 1 (2005-2006) === ==References== Go Diego Go
